Tosh.Description:
Tosh is a mysterious terran spectre described as "pseudo-Rastafarian". He is a skillful martial artist. Carrying the terrorist personality, he is also the representing figure of Dominion's Spectre Project. He can use Mind Blast, Psionic Shield, Shadow Strike, and Devour. Tosh will join the battle togeather with an invaded and crashed Battlecruiser. When Tosh is dead, he will revive at the same location after 60 seconds.

Can attack the ground and air.
Tosh.Name: Gabriel Tosh

ToshSpectre.Description:
Infiltration unit. Can use Ultrasonic Pulse and Cloak. Can also call down Tactical Nukes built at the Ghost Academy.

Can attack ground and air units.
ToshSpectre.Name: Spectre

ToshReaper.Description:
Raider. Capable of jumping up and down cliffs. Throws explosive mines.

Can attack ground units.
ToshReaper.Name: Death Head

D8Charge.Description: Timed explosive that does heavy area damage.
D8Charge.Name: G-4 Charge

ToshHeroBattlecruiser.Description:
Silence Mors was once stolen by most wanted criminal by Federacy and fallen into the grasp of Tosh in a mission. This Battlecruiser has been adapted in Dylarian shipyards and added with more powerful firepower and fusion reactor, being capable of frequently use Tactic Jump and Yamato Cannon. Thus, it becomes the supportive capital ship of Tosh's Shadow Blade agents.

Can attack the ground and air.
ToshHeroBattlecruiser.Name: Silence Mors

ToshBattlecruiser.Description:
The stolen dominion Elite Supreme Battlecruiser. This powerful warship can use warpjump and release firepower to surrounding enemy units.

Can attack the ground and air.
ToshBattlecruiser.Name: The Stolen Dominion Battlecrusier
